4. GUI: IIS Manager \f2\u8594?\f1  \f0 Sites \f2\u8594?\f1  \f0 Add Website\'85 (set path, port 80/443, host name).\par
5. Import/assign SSL cert under Server Certificates and in Bindings for HTTPS.\par
6. Baseline hardening & housekeeping\par
7. Group Policy: Create baseline GPOs (password/lockout, firewall, audit, WSUS, RDP restrictions) via gpmc.msc.\par
8. Backups: Install Windows Server Backup, schedule daily backup incl. System State.\par
\b PowerShell:\b0\par
1. wbadmin enable backup -addtarget:{{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "\\\\\\\\NAS\\\\Backups\\\\SRV-APP01"}}{\fldrslt{\\\\NAS\\Backups\\SRV-APP01\ul0\cf0}}}}\f0\fs28  -include:C:,SystemState -schedule:21:00 -quiet\par
2. Monitoring & logs: Configure Event Forwarding, set performance counters/alerts.\par
3. Anti-malware: Deploy Defender or your enterprise AV.\par
