\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj After installation, click the notification flag in Server Manager.\par
