\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj Choose Download updates, drivers, and optional features (recommended).\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}Enter product key.\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}Select the correct edition (Standard/Datacenter, Core/Desktop Experience).\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b 5. Choose Upgrade Option\b0\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj When prompted, select:\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}Keep personal files and apps (this performs the in-place upgrade).\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}If you select "Nothing," it will be a clean install (not upgrade).\b\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj 6. Accept License Terms\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b0 Read and accept Microsoft Software License Terms.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b 7. Compatibility Check\b0\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj Setup runs a check for application and driver compatibility.\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}Fix any issues reported (e.g., uninstall unsupported apps).\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b 8. Install Upgrade\b0\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj Click Install.\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}The upgrade process copies files, installs features, and migrates roles.\par
