\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b 9. Post-Upgrade Configuration\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b0 Log in with the same credentials.\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}Verify that roles (AD DS, DNS, DHCP, IIS, etc.) are working.\par
{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}Reapply group policies, firewall rules, and settings if needed.\par
