Open ADUC Tool\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b0 Go to Server Manager \f2\u8594?\f0  Tools \f2\u8594?\f0  Active Directory Users and Computers.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b Select OU (Organizational Unit)\b0\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj Expand your domain \f2\u8594?\f0  choose the OU where you want to create the user.\par

