\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj Right-click the OU \f2\u8594?\f0  New \f2\u8594?\f0  User.\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\b Enter User Details\b0\par

\pard{\pntext\f7\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf7\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj Fill in First name, Last name, User logon name (e.g., jdoe@example.com\lang1033 ). \par
